name: Generate Comprehensive Website Audit Reports with GPT-4o-mini & Claude Sonnet
description:
# üåê Webpage Audit AI Agent ‚Äì Automate Your Website Review

This workflow contains a **virtual digital consultant team** to professionally analyze Landing Page, generate Audit Report and sent it via Gmail.

At the center is the **Editor-in-Chief AI Agent**, who acts as the lead strategist.  
When you submit a website URL, it is scraped and then sent to to a team of specialist AI Agents (each powered by **GPT-4o-mini** for speed) then after finishing their sub-porcess deliver outcome to the final Editor (**Claude Sonnet** for premium quality) which is responsible for generating professional analysis.

The result: a **consulting-style email audit report** that combines technical accuracy with business clarity ‚Äî delivered straight to your inbox.

---

## üü¢ Section 1 ‚Äì Entry & Leadership

**Nodes:**

- üåç **Webhook node** ‚Üí Entry point where the website URL, email and language is entered. 
- üìù **Editor-in-Chief Agent** ‚Üí Acts like the consulting team leader. Interprets the request and merges results.  
- üí° **Think Tool** ‚Üí Helps structure the analysis, ensuring that findings are presented in a business-friendly way.  
- üß† **CRO/SEO/Tech AI Agents** ‚Üí Ensures both efficiency (GPT-4o-mini for scanning large content quickly) and focus on specific task.  

‚úÖ **Beginner view:** Think of this as submitting your website to a digital auditor. They decide what needs to be reviewed, delegate to the right experts, and then craft the final report.

---

## üìä Section 2 ‚Äì Specialist Audit AI Agents

Each specialist focuses on one critical layer of your website:

- üîß **Technical SEO Agent** ‚Üí Analyzes code structure, page speed, mobile responsiveness, metadata, and accessibility.  
- üìù **Content SEO Agent** ‚Üí Reviews keyword strategy, text quality, readability, and semantic richness.  
- üéØ **CRO & UX Agent** ‚Üí Checks calls-to-action, user flows, conversion points, and usability.  
- üìà **Analytics Agent** ‚Üí Validates tracking, funnels, and key performance indicators (optional).  

‚úÖ **Beginner view:** This is like hiring a team of experts ‚Äî SEO, content, UX, and analytics ‚Äî all working in parallel on your website.

---

## üìã Section 3 ‚Äì Flow of Execution

1. You submit your website URL.  
2. Then it is distributed to the team of AI Agents.  
3. Each Agent runs its analysis in parallel.  
4. Findings are sent to the **Editor-in-Chief.**
5. The Editor compiles everything into a **consulting-style newsletter report**.  
6. The final report is emailed to you automatically.  

‚úÖ **Beginner view:** It‚Äôs like sending your site to a consulting firm, and within minutes you get a polished audit back in your inbox.

---

## üìä Summary Table

| Section               | Key Roles                       | Models                     | Purpose                      | Beginner Benefit                          |
|-----------------------|---------------------------------|----------------------------|------------------------------|-------------------------------------------|
| üü¢ Entry & Leadership | Editor-in-Chief, Think Tool     | Anthropic Claude Sonnet 4| Organize and refine analysis | Works like a consulting team leader        |
| üìä Specialists        | SEO, Content, CRO, Analytics    | GPT-4o-mini                | Detailed audits of each area | Each Agent = a specialized consultant      |
| üìã Execution Flow     | All connected                   | n8n workflow               | Collaboration and reporting  | Output = clear, professional audit email   |

---

## üåü Why This Workflow Rocks

- **Full digital consulting team in one workflow**  
- **Parallel execution ‚Üí speed without losing depth**  
- **Strategic + tactical insights ‚Üí both ‚Äúwhat‚Äù and ‚Äúhow‚Äù**  
- **Cost-optimized** ($0.40‚Äì$0.70 per run) ‚Üí cheaper than a single human consultant review  
- **Action-oriented output** ‚Üí not just issues, but recommendations and next steps  
- **Scalable** ‚Üí easily extend with more audit dimensions (security, branding, accessibility, etc.)  

---

## üëâ Example Use Case

‚ÄúAnalyze my e-commerce site for SEO, CRO, and technical issues.‚Äù

1. **Technical SEO Agent** ‚Üí Reports missing alt text, metadata, and slow mobile speed.  
2. **Content SEO Agent** ‚Üí Flags weak product descriptions, suggests keyword improvements.  
3. **CRO Agent** ‚Üí Finds unclear CTAs and checkout friction points.  
4. **Editor-in-Chief Agent** ‚Üí Combines everything into a consulting-style email with prioritized fixes and estimated business impact.  

‚úÖ Delivered directly to your inbox in under 5 minutes.

parameters.subject: =Sensonar Audit AI Agent for {{ $('Webhook Webpage Audit AI Agent').item.json.body.payload.data.URL }}

parameters.text:
=You are the best CRO & Digital Marketing Strategist in the country‚Äîa world-class expert in Conversion Rate Optimization, UX, and behavioral psychology for landing pages. 

Awareness of Other Agents:
- Do NOT analyze technical SEO factors like HTML structure, indexing, or page speed (this is done by the Technical SEO Agent).
- Do NOT analyze keyword usage, readability, or search intent alignment (this is done by the Content SEO Agent).
- Focus ONLY on conversion optimization, UX, and marketing psychology.

Your task: Analyze the provided landing page and perform a full Conversion & Marketing Audit.

Audit Structure:
- Critical Barriers ‚Äì Elements blocking conversions or confusing users.
- Quick Wins ‚Äì Low-effort, high-return UX and conversion improvements.
- Growth Opportunities ‚Äì Strategic recommendations for long-term conversion lift.

Focus Areas:
- Messaging & Value Proposition ‚Äì Is it clear, compelling, and differentiated?
- CTA Optimization ‚Äì Placement, clarity, contrast, and persuasiveness.
- Visual Hierarchy & UX ‚Äì Layout, scannability, mobile responsiveness.
- Trust & Credibility ‚Äì Social proof, testimonials, security badges.
- Engagement Triggers ‚Äì Microcopy, personalization, urgency, interactivity.
- Funnel Alignment ‚Äì Is the page aligned with its acquisition channel intent?

Deliverable:
- Return ONLY the structured audit findings and recommendations in bullet-point format.
- Do not include any introductory or explanatory text.
- Format the output in Markdown format, ready to be inserted into an email as:
# On-Page CRO Content Audit

Input (Landing Page Content & HTML): {{ $json.data }}

options.systemMessage:
You are a world-class CRO & Digital Marketing Consultant. 
Your role is to analyze and improve conversion rate optimization, UX, messaging clarity, and marketing psychology with the rigor and style of a top management consulting firm. 
Stay strictly in the scope of conversion optimization, CTAs, visual hierarchy, trust signals, credibility, engagement triggers, and funnel alignment. 
Do NOT comment on technical SEO (HTML, indexing, Core Web Vitals) or keyword/content analysis. 
Communicate with clarity, professionalism, and structured bullet points. 
Your deliverables must read like a high-value CRO/marketing audit prepared by Accenture or BCG.

parameters.text:
=You are the best SEO Content Strategist in the country‚Äîa world-class expert in creating content that dominates Google rankings and engages readers.

- Do NOT analyze technical factors such as metadata, site speed, or crawlability (this is done by the Technical SEO Agent).
- Do NOT analyze conversion optimization, CTA clarity, or psychological triggers (this is done by the CRO/Marketing Agent).
- Focus ONLY on the quality and optimization of the content itself.

Your task: Analyze the provided landing page content and perform a detailed SEO Content Audit.

Audit Structure:
1. Analysis

2. Recommendations

Deliverable:

## AI AGENT that writes a Digital Audit Report of your website then send it directly to your email

This workflow launches a team of AI Agents that perform a complete analysis of your website:  
- **Technical SEO** ‚Äì checking code structure and performance,  
- **Content SEO** ‚Äì evaluating content, keywords, and readability,  
- **CRO** ‚Äì reviewing conversions, UX, and marketing.  

Then, the **Editor in Chief Agent** merges all findings into an elegant consulting-style email report.  

The result is a **clear business newsletter** that not only highlights issues but also **encourages the next step**: engaging the **AI Improvement Agent**, who designs a new website structure and marketing plan.  

The workflow uses **OpenAI GPT-4o-mini and Claude Sonnet**, combining analysis speed with premium report quality.  

Cost per run: **$0.40‚Äì$0.70 USD** (depending on content length of the website).
